 BERWYN：“我们正处于人类自由受到限制的疯狂时代” https://www.nme.com/news/music/berwyn-mercury-prize-2024-interview-who-am-i-3779227?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=berwyn-mercury-prize-2024-interview-who-我-我Andrew TrendellTue, 30 Jul 2024 11:50:02 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsNME RadarMercury PrizeRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3779227 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BERWYN 出席 2024 年水星奖颁奖典礼（摄影：Jeff Spicer/Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位双水星奖提名者向《NME》讲述了人们对移民态度的转变，以及他今年最喜欢的获奖者</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/berwyn-mercury-prize-2024-interview-who-am-i-3779227">BERWYN 的帖子：“我们正处于人类自由受到限制的疯狂时代”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BERWYN 出席 2024 年水星奖颁奖典礼（摄影：Jeff Spicer/Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/BERYWYN_MERCURY_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BERWYN">BERWYN</a>接受<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了影响他获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>提名的新专辑《我是谁》的政治动荡，以及他今年最喜欢的获奖作品。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-berwyn-interview-who-am-i-3774853"><strong>阅读更多：</strong>封面上——爱至上：伯温说出了他的真相</a></li></ul><p>这位出生于特立尼达、罗姆福德长大的说唱歌手、制作人、歌手和词曲作者上周出现在水星奖颁奖典礼的红地毯上（7 月 25 日星期四）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-check-out-the-shortlisted-nominees-here-3777869">宣布他已入围广</a>受好评的 2023 年专辑《我是谁》——与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CORINNE-BAILEY-RAE">Corinne Bailey Rae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/GHETTS">Ghetts</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">English Teacher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-gibbons">Beth Gibbons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">Barry Can&#39;t Swim</a>等唱片的竞争。</p><p>这标志着<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-berwyn-interview-who-am-i-3774853">这位新近<em>NME</em>封面明星</a>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/berwyn-mercury-prize-2021-performance-interview-new-album-tour-3043305">2021 年凭借混音作品“DEMOTAPE/VEGA”入围候选名单</a>后，第二次获得 Mercury 认可。</p><p> BERWYN 在回应今年入围名单的其他成员时告诉<em>NME</em> ：“这肯定是一场激烈的竞争。上次我被提名为混音带，这次我被提名为专辑。那里有很多严肃的艺术作品；这可不是说笑。我在这里，我还活着，我很快乐。</p><p> “我读过很多评论家的评论。音乐评论家的意见对我来说很重要，因为他们是专家并且知道他们在谈论什么，但除此之外，这只是噪音。这就是这张专辑的风格——忽略噪音——所以我必须继续这样做。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C941JGBIRGD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" sty